{"tid":1983121,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"剛剛去了打座修行，我分享一下其中我悟到的事。","createTime":"2020-04-21T15:08:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T00:58:52.000Z","uid":74425,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3f9eb1367ea4634ef784cfa381d5871e36c11dfa","tid":1983121,"uid":74425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T15:08:30.000Z","msg":"1 . 我是一個stimulator framer，我的工作是去體驗（farming),what I fram is feeling+experience in reality, which are seed. The growing stuff is 存在意識（在四維dimemsion的空間中，我們稱這個為回憶。<br />\n2. 我在睡著時，會以為我在三維空間（即物理世界）中的我，是真的我，其實不是，這只是你的幻覺而已，就像你玩遊戲的角色，就像你帶上VR眼鏡是看到的東西，就像rick and morty其中一集morty在玩一隻人生遊戲。<br />\n3. 我在三維空間既是自由的，又是命定的。自由是指我能隨意選擇經驗什麼，命定是指無論我經歷了什麼，我最終也能實踐真我。<br />\n4. 我有心中有一座監獄，困著我們，透過我們的想像（想像這個moment會有多壞）。逃離這個監獄的方法是：勇氣、可由成為一個觀察自己感覺和心智的我來產生。"},{"pid":"c8625b1cc653e42e37b7b3bb0bf500cb641bc5d0","tid":1983121,"uid":74425,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T15:08:57.000Z","msg":"補充第二點：你可以想像睡著為：你連續在玩一百年的vr game，久得你忘記了自己其實在玩遊戲。"},{"pid":"3747a652ab577cb6498e61c4036068eed4734c81","tid":1983121,"uid":74425,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T15:12:30.000Z","msg":"我很可笑，因為我經常一百分投入我在玩的遊戲角色<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/