core":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f9eb1367ea4634ef784cfa381d5871e36c11dfa","tid":1983121,"uid":74425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T15:08:30.000Z","msg":"1 . 我是一個stimulator framer，我的工作是去體驗（farming),what I fram is feeling+experience in reality, which are seed. The growing stuff is 存在意識（在四維dimemsion的空間中，我們稱這個為回憶。<br />\n2. 我在睡著時，會以為我在三維空間（即物理世界）中的我，是真的我，其實不是，這只是你的幻覺而已，就像你玩遊戲的角色，就像你帶上VR眼鏡是看到的東西，就像rick and morty其中一集morty在玩一隻人生遊戲。<br />\n3. 我在三維空間既是自由的，又是命定的。自由是指我能隨意選擇經驗什麼，命定是指無論我經歷了什麼，我最終也能實踐真我。<br />\n4. 我有心中有一座監獄，困著我們，透過我們的想像（想像這個moment會有多壞）。逃離這個監獄的方法是：勇氣、可由成為一個觀察自己感覺和心智的我來產生。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T16:21:55.000Z","msg":"nice bro"},{"pid":"b436308af9a94a6c1b42c4071ebbb68e19cfdf25","tid":1983121,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be7d66a7d3547bff99b37d274173d642997bb02f","tid":1983121,"uid":74425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T16:15:21.000Z","msg":"要消化，我input完再output，出黎你睇下了解得岩唔岩。<br />\n舉個例子：<br />\n我現在訓係張床到，假設我既人生縮到得番呢個範圍去簡化討論先：想像一下我在這張床有很多個我在做不同的事，例如訓教，做愛，食飯，看書，玩電腦。我開始感受到自己是一粒粒的黑點訓教的黑點連結在做愛的黑點，又連結食飯的黑點，慢慢形成了一個網，這個網就是我。最後我將當下既體驗化成一粒新點在這個網中。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T16:25:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有少少偏<br />\n<br />\n你應該會發現有 something 係係咁多個經驗中都係不變不動<br />\n當你感覺到就安住係入面"},{"pid":"26f6a93f573bd0812cc6d6e639a5cfc6dc406532","tid":1983121,"uid":266876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e50f960f0569d3b312e179a3072e53fd12a455b9","tid":1983121,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd7977ad70c0ef305ded1e1e495fc7f52daad0a0","tid":1983121,"uid":74425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"412a2eb53b5fb85338c0a8fea16efd1e24f6d34a","tid":1983121,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T15:51:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我以前有用呢個方法<br />\n不過我想像自己既一切，肉身思維心識入左個喼<br />\n然後掉撚左佢<br />\n<br />\n依家唔會用呢個方法"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T16:03:32.000Z","msg":"wow<br />\n剛剛試了這個方法。好有效，直接。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T16:09:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n畀多個方法你，係更直接感受本質<br />\n<br />\n你想像番你呢生人所經驗既時間線上既經驗<br />\n一次過出現，即係將時間壓縮成現在<br />\n全部經驗係齊到<br />\n你會發覺有一個「存在」同時貫串全部經驗<br />\n而果個「存在」係不動既，平安既，自然既，靜既<br />\n<br />\n可以既話將當下呢一刻既經驗包含入去"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T16:29:26.000Z","msg":"要試 試 先<br />\n多謝"},{"pid":"14c190ecbcd2fcedb60f0fce52880c10ddec6b90","tid":1983121,"uid":266876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94c653b6ffcb09abc194a1bf6f38882b03e46137","tid":1983121,"uid":74425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6e863f6dede1a96aabfe01ccfa8c7926113872f4","tid":1983121,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d1d14487f72a256ec978c386356913d915f69e9","tid":1983121,"uid":74425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T16:04:36.000Z","msg":"你有無netflix？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T16:09:51.000Z","msg":"點解咁問 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T16:16:08.000Z","msg":"琴日出左套卡通中文叫午夜福音<br />\n第5集個idea係我個post既野"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T16:31:09.000Z","msg":"the midmight gospel"},{"pid":"28e24a41d4d428c4b04ae09e98f2b6cf6d50f5b5","tid":1983121,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26f6a93f573bd0812cc6d6e639a5cfc6dc406532","tid":1983121,"uid":266876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e50f960f0569d3b312e179a3072e53fd12a455b9","tid":1983121,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd7977ad70c0ef305ded1e1e495fc7f52daad0a0","tid":1983121,"uid":74425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T16:03:32.000Z","msg":"wow<br />\n剛剛試